# 🚀 C++ HTTP Server using Crow

A lightweight and blazing-fast HTTP server built in C++ using the [Crow](https://github.com/CrowCpp/Crow) web framework. This project demonstrates how to create simple RESTful routes and handle HTTP requests using modern C++17 features.

## 📌 Features

- ⚡ Built with **Crow** – a C++ microframework inspired by Flask
- 🛣️ Custom routes like `/`, `/status`, `/your_name`
- 🧩 Modular and clean project structure
- 💥 Fast and minimal – perfect for learning C++ web backends

